cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.GT, cs.HC, cs.MM 

This paper deals with computer vision and graphics, specifically with estimating indoor lighting from a single RGB image. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves graphics and rendering, which suggests cs.GR (Computer Graphics) as a likely category. The method proposed in the paper does not require any geometry information, which could fall under cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory). The paper also includes a user study, which could be categorized under cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Finally, the paper's approach can be used for augmented reality applications, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia).
